<br>
&quot;Find the woman whose blood comes from this bottle.&quot; Morcrin said, as he let a drop fall onto the held out palms of the two assasins. Both of the faceless men closed their fists as if feeling the essence of Minru through her blood; their eyes closed while using their unusual abilities to track their prey. &quot;This woman may become....an unfortunate liability, one I cannot afford. Watch for her to leave her home. She has too many allies to attack her within the temple of shadows, although if you can find a way to enter unknown....then mutilate her quietly.&quot; Morcrin looked at the two ghastly men for a moment. &quot;You know the binding of the Plague Bringer keeps you from revealing any information should you be captured....&quot; the Necromancer paused. &quot;but if anything should happen to where you are captured alive....then you know what silent spell to cast to make things more...interesting for your captors.&quot;<br>
<br>
Out of the cave ran two horrid men, hunting for a dark elf woman by the essence of her blood. Two silent, faceless men with no fear and no compassion. Two men seeking not to kill Minru but worse, to cut away her sight and voice with magic blades and mystic disease. Disease no cleric could cure; a special &quot;kiss&quot; from the Plague Bringer. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=mysticlioness>MysticLioness</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Demon Damsel<br>
