<br>
Minru, ussta abbil. Please respond...do not leave us. ~she held Minru close to her as she watched her wound begin to heal. A sigh of relieve that it had worked or at least helped some. Her wound closed and she gently brushed Minru's hair from her face, knowing Minru is still too weak to talk, she held her rocking~<br>
<br>
 <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.eqguild.net/guilds/Eviah/Ezentari1.JPG" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub150.ezboard.com/bevilchicksinc" target="top">Proud to be an Evil Chick</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ikatsui>Ikatsui</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/10/03 1:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1208.topic&index=27>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dreams in the Dark ((GORE WARNING!))</span><hr size=1> Making his way into the commons from the foreign quarter, Ikatsui notices how few guards there are at the gates.  He stops to speak to one and learns that some sickness has the Priests busy this evening.  He nods and moves on.  While passing over the bridge he stops and looks down into the waters for a moment lost in thought.<br>
<br>
A sight catches his attention and he spies two women down by the water, holding one another.  He shrugs for its not uncommon for two lovers to meet near the waters like so.  He turns away only to stop when he hears...<br>
<br>
&quot;Minru, ussta abbil. Please respond...do not leave us...&quot;<br>
<br>
Minru!?!  He turns and stares intently at the two women... one wears a white robe... the one laying in the arms of the other.  He jumps down to the rock ledge and makes his way quickly to them, his booted feet upon the stone alerts the woman holding the prone Minru... Ezentari?  She looks up to him, blood dripping from her mouth and her arm torn open.  Minru lay unmoving, a slash in her shoulder... her face pale with a light layer of sweat and blood covering her.<br>
<br>
Ikatsui looks to Ezentari and then back to Minru.  He summons the divine magic of the Father to heal Minru.  Though the wound itself heals over... the magic seemed unable to penetrate the deep parts of the cut.<br>
<br>
&quot;Help me with her, we must get her to the Temple, there we can look into this wound and be away from any remaning danger here.&quot; With that he picks up Minru carefully holding her close.  <br>
<br>
<br>
&quot;Carry her and I will watch over you both from the shadows.&quot;  Then Ezentari slips into the shadows quickly vanishing from sight.<br>
<br>
As Ikatsui passes the gate guard to the commons they stand alertly as he looks to them hatred written across his features.  He ignores them as he makes his way to the Temple.  Along the way he watches Ezentari slip from the shadows behind a commoner who strayed to close to them, his body left in the rocks... only a husk of his former self.<br>
<br>
Upon entering the Temple he carries Minru to a small chamber with a bed and table.  He summons an acolyte to find the High Priest and to being fresh cloth, water and a robe.<br>
<br>
Turning back to Minru he pulls off her robe to look at the wound.  When the acolyte returns he cleans the wound and the area around it as Minru begins to stir.<br>
<br>
&quot;Any pain you feel Minru will be as easy as I can make it for you.  I wish to make sure the wound is not poisoned or festering inside.&quot;  He begins calling upon the divine for the magics needed to purify the body of poisons, of disease, of curses... as he finishes he tenderly looks over the wound.  He looks up, knowing that Ezentari is with them.<br>
<br>
&quot;Something is not right... this wound has the marks of a disease that I do not believe I could have cured... but it is gone now.  Her body is healed though... but she will still be weak.  We need to find what happened.&quot;<br>
<br>
Standing he moves across the room as the High Priest enters.  They speak softly then Ikatsui turns to Ezentari who slips from the shadows.<br>
<br>
&quot;I must go.  I am going to seek out some answers to this.  The Priests here will watch over and protect her and any here with her.  Ezentari... we will find out what happened.&quot;  Leaning in close to her he whispers... &quot;There are some components that the Priests will need in case this is the touch of the Lord Bert... of the Plague.&quot;<br>
<br>
With that he leaves them be as the acolyte moves in to clean Minru and dress her in a clean robe.<br>
 <p>Ikatsui,<br>
Priest of Innoruuk<br>
Member of the League of Shadows<br>
